    <listitem>
<!-- 
     <para>
      Avoid <quote>cannot GetMultiXactIdMembers() during recovery</> error
      (&Aacute;lvaro Herrera)
     </para>
-->
<para>
避免<quote>cannot GetMultiXactIdMembers() during recovery</>错误
      (&Aacute;lvaro Herrera)
</para>
