</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- 
     <para>
      Fix namespace handling in <function>xpath()</> (Ali Akbar)
     </para>
-->
<para>
修复<function>xpath()</>中的命名空间处理 (Ali Akbar)
</para>

<!-- 
     <para>
      Previously, the <type>xml</> value resulting from
      an <function>xpath()</> call would not have namespace declarations if
