</para>

<!-- 
     <para>
      This mistake could result in transient errors in queries being
      executed in hot standby.
     </para>
-->
<para>
这个错误会导致在热备中执行查询时的瞬态错误。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- 
