-->
<para>
修复恢复逻辑不适当的忽略了<literal>COMMIT/ABORT PREPARED</>
的WAL记录的几个情况 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>

<!-- 
     <para>
      The most notable oversight was
      that <varname>recovery_min_apply_delay</> failed to delay application
