<para>
修复<literal>EXISTS(SELECT * FROM zero_column_table)</literal>
的解析器崩溃 (Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- 
     <para>
      Fix possible crash due to invalid plan for nested sub-selects, such
