     </para>
-->
<para>
为<literal>COPY TO STDOUT/FROM STDIN</>期间的失败，改善<application>libpq</>
和<application>psql</>中的错误处理 (Tom Lane)
</para>

<!-- 
     <para>
      In particular this fixes an infinite loop that could occur in 9.2 and
      up if the server connection was lost during <literal>COPY FROM
      STDIN</>.  Variants of that scenario might be possible in older
      versions, or with other client applications.
     </para>
-->
<para>
特别的，这修复了一个在9.2及更高版本中可能发生的无限循环，
如果在<literal>COPY FROM STDIN</>期间丢失服务器连接。
这种情况的变体可能会在较老版本或其他客户端应用中发生。
