-->
<para>
在<filename>contrib/isn</>中，修复ISMN值的检查位的不正确计算 (Fabien Coelho)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- 
     <para>
      Fix <filename>contrib/pg_stat_statement</>'s handling
      of <literal>CURRENT_DATE</> and related constructs (Kyotaro
      Horiguchi)
     </para>
-->
<para>
修复<filename>contrib/pg_stat_statement</>对<literal>CURRENT_DATE</>
和相关构造的处理 (Kyotaro Horiguchi)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- 
     <para>
      Ensure client-code-only installation procedure works as documented
      (Peter Eisentraut)
     </para>
-->
<para>
确保仅客户端的编码安装程序像记录中那样运行 (Peter Eisentraut)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!-- 
     <para>
      In Mingw and Cygwin builds, install the <application>libpq</> DLL
