<para>
   不要在<command>DROP RULE IF NOT EXISTS</> and <command>DROP TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS</>中修改输入解析树(Tom Lane)
</para>


     <!--
<para>
      This mistake would cause errors if a cached statement of one of these
