     </para>
-->
<para>
   修复<application>libpq</>的<function>lo_import()</>和<function>lo_export()</>函数以正确报告文件I/O错误(Tom Lane)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Fix <application>ecpg</>'s processing of nested structure pointer
      variables (Muhammad Usama)
     </para>
-->
<para>
    修复嵌套结构指针变量的<application>ecpg</>处理(Muhammad Usama)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Fix <application>ecpg</>'s <function>ecpg_get_data</> function to
