     </para>
-->
<para>
   修复<application>ecpg</>的<function>ecpg_get_data</>函数以正确处理数组(Michael Meskes)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Prevent <application>pg_upgrade</> from trying to process TOAST tables
