    通过设置新群集中<varname>synchronous_commit</>到<literal>off</>提升<application>pg_upgrade</>性能(Bruce Momjian)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Make <filename>contrib/pageinspect</>'s btree page inspection
