    </listitem>

    <listitem>
     <!--
<para>
      Work around unportable behavior of <literal>malloc(0)</> and
      <literal>realloc(NULL, 0)</> (Tom Lane)
     </para>
-->
<para>
     解决<literal>malloc(0)</>和<literal>realloc(NULL, 0)</>不可移植操作(Tom Lane)
